## 🔄 Complete Flow Diagram

```
                    UPLOAD FLOW
                    ───────────
You upload PDF
      ↓
App reads the file
      ↓
Splits into chunks (1000 characters each)
      ↓
OpenAI converts each chunk to numbers (embeddings)
      ↓
Numbers saved in Pinecone ✅


                    QUERY FLOW
                    ──────────
You type a question
      ↓
OpenAI converts question to numbers
      ↓
Pinecone finds top 5 most similar chunks
      ↓
Chunks + Question sent to GPT-4o
      ↓
GPT-4o writes answer using only those chunks
      ↓
Answer + Sources shown in chat ✅
```

