| PDF | Research papers, reports, books |
| TXT | Notes, articles, documentation |
| Markdown | Technical docs, wikis |
| CSV | Data files, spreadsheets |

---

## 💡 Why is This Useful?

Without this app → You manually read 100 pages to find one answer.

With this app → You ask a question and get the answer in seconds with the exact source.

This technique is called **RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation)** and it is used by companies like Google, Microsoft, and many startups to build AI assistants on top of their own private data.

